<p><b>Guidance</b> is a <a href="/wiki/Divination" title="Divination">divination</a> <a href="/wiki/Cantrip" title="Cantrip" class="mw-redirect">cantrip</a> available to <a href="/wiki/Cleric" title="Cleric">clerics</a> and <a href="/wiki/Druid" title="Druid">druids</a>.<sup id="cite_ref-spellLists_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-spellLists-1">[2]</a></sup>
</p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Description"> Description </span></h2>
<p>You touch a willing <a href="/wiki/Creature" title="Creature">creature</a>, granting it a <a href="/wiki/Dice" title="Dice">1d4</a> bonus to one <a href="/wiki/Ability_Scores" title="Ability Scores">ability check</a> of its choice. The spell then ends. The target can roll the die before or after making the check.<sup id="cite_ref-spellDesc_0-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-spellDesc-0">[1]</a></sup>
</p>
